# Starfield background

System spans:
- Layout + import map + debug markup: `base.njk`
- Bootstrap / gating: `static/js/starfield-bg.js`
- Scene + controls: `static/experiments/starfield/*.js`
- Styles: `_includes/css/index.css` (`html.has-starfield-bg`)

## Rules

- Keep Three.js import map in `base.njk` aligned with `static/experiments/starfield/index.html`.
- Keep gating logic consistent between `base.njk` (inline) and `starfield-bg.js`.
- Keep debug panel IDs in sync with `app.js` (e.g. `#debug-panel`, controls, perf UI).
- Do not break shared structure between site and experiment.

See README files for full details.